        <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_no-frontmatter.dita" xtrc="p:4;71:12">The file contains a byte-order mark (BOM) or non-UTF-8 characters
        before the <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_no-frontmatter.dita" xtrc="codeph:5;72:28">---</codeph> delimiter.</p>
